  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large sous-vide-safe saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the crushed Slovakian black bread and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring occasionally, until golden brown.','Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.','Add the Slovakian bean sprouts and cook for 3-4 minutes, until they start to soften.',",
    "Add the vegetable stock and bring to a simmer.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh dill and lemon juice.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Remove from heat and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve immediately."
